nded play, ''For the Feel'', in 2014, from Dead Oceans. The group released another [[studio album]], ''Welcome the Worms'', on April 1, 2016,<ref name=\"AllMusic Review Two\">{{cite web |first=Heather |last=Phares |title=''Welcome the Worms'' \u2013 Bleached : Review |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/welcome-the-worms-mw0002911783 |publisher=[[AllMusic]] |accessdate=April 10, 2016 |date=April 1, 2016}}</ref> with Dead Oceans.<ref name=\"Metacritic Second\">{{cite web |author=[[CBS Interactive]] |title=Critic reviews for Welcome the Worms by Bleached |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/welcome-the-worms/bleached/critic-reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=April 10, 2016}}</ref> The album peaked on the Heatseekers Albums chart at No. 15,<ref name=\"Heatseekers Albums\">{{cite web|author=''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]''|title=Bleached - Chart history (Top Heatseekers Albums)|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]] |url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/1557231/bleached/chart?f=324 |accessdate=April 13, 2016}}</ref> while it placed on the [[Independent Albums]] chart at No. 46.<ref name=\"Independent Albums\">{{cite web|author=''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]''|title=Bleached - Chart history (Independent Albums)|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]] |url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/1557231/bleached/chart?f=326 |accessdate=April 13, 2016}}</ref>\n\n== Members ==\n\n[[File:Jennifer Clavin of Bleached at The Great Escape, May 2016 (2).jpg|thumb|right|Jennifer Clavin performing with the band in May 2016]]\n*'''Jennifer Clavin''' \u2013 lead vocals, guitar, synth\n{{Short description|\u2013 lead guitar, bass}}\n*'''Jessica Clavin''' \u2013 lead guitar, bass\n{{Short description|\u2013 drums, percussion}}\n*'''Nick Pillot''' \u2013 drums, percussion\n\n== Discography ==\n\n=== Studio albums ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of studio albums, with selected chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" styl